## ecology idea credit: [ecological](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/ecological)

[x] grass now drops mixed seeds (mixed seeds most often wont grow into anything besides 95% grass, however, they have a chance to grow into a random regular crop)
[x] you can find crops in the world in pathes like grass directly on the ground no tilled soil required (you still need to till soil to plant seeds)
[x] carrot seeds & potato seeds (you can still plant a potato or a carrot)
[x] pollination (works like bonemeal)
[x] reward treating animals ethicly (large pasture, water accsessibilty, etc), ex: more yeald
[x] grass blocks have a chance to grow short grass above them naturally - And short grass is able to grow into tall grass.
[x] make carrot seed texture
[x] make potato seed texture
[x] make mixed seed texture
[x] make grass grow a bit slower and work more like a weed but not grow in real time, like crops kinda slow
[x] make desire paths easier to get and erode much slower

